    {
        "content": "<p>(It's worth mentioning that this dependence on the compiler will show up in <code>#print axioms</code>, you'll see <code>Lean.ofReduceBool</code>)</p>",
        "id": 505862261,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1742055413
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'd have suggested <code>norm_num</code>, but it seems like no one wrote a norm num plugin for IsSquare yet.</p>",
        "id": 505862288,
